{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6e8b73eea4","title":"攻击幹部政策的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dac5489b97","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"6e8b73eea4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4a589fcf4c","name":"黄盛业"},{"id":"8c480950cf","name":"钱端升"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0cccceec61","type":"title","text":"攻击干部政策的右派言论北京政法学院 张景明 赵日月 王革 康德琯 林道廉 蔡群先 陈守铭 尹孝松 李涵林","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"934fde5971","type":"authors","text":"黄盛业钱端升","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"785162749c","type":"subtitle","text":"[钱端升：北京政法学院院长]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"f87ad14894","type":"subtitle","text":"(1)关于德才兼备的干部政策","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"bb6250aaa1","type":"paragraph","text":"张景明说：“德顶什么用，光凭德什么也干不了，只有拿出货色来才能建设社会主义。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"a66fd9d29d","type":"paragraph","text":"赵日月说：“过去保送的留学生都是些“笨蛋””有的同学反驳说：“过去保送党团员是为了保证政治质量。”赵日月马上反驳说：“政治质量只要看历史清楚，不包括政治觉悟………党团员仅仅是个符号，并不等于政治质量高。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"36ed8ae9a5","type":"paragraph","text":"王革说：我院人事制度是“重德不重才，而德只要看你是不是党团员。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"eedfeaf094","type":"paragraph","text":"康德琯说：“我也觉得学校重德不重才，因此我觉得领导上对德的看法也是宗派主义的。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"43a77c4821","type":"subtitle","text":"(2)关于人事工作","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"14637ec167","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事处好象在群众之上不受群众的监督，是掌握别人，支配别人的机关。”(林道廉)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"a8846ee3bd","type":"paragraph","text":"“精简机构，裁减冗员，对待遇不合理者要调正，真正作到“按劳取酬”，叫那些不称职者下台，让位于贤，人事工作不要神秘化。应交年高德昭人公正在群众中享有威信的人担任。”(赵日月)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"0f1d6688ff","type":"paragraph","text":"“消灭学校人事臃肿的现象，撤消人事二科，反对吃闲饭等一些不必要的机构(党团工作人员一定要兼任行政工作，无功不受禄。)”(蔡群先写，陈守铭改)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"70ad3fadce","type":"subtitle","text":"(3)关于汇报鉴定制度","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"3a28b3b407","type":"paragraph","text":"“我认为党的汇报、人事制度就会产生宗派主义，因为党只限于党员。”(尹孝松)","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"72739fadbc","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党是特务机关、共产党员汇报是特务行为。”(李涵林)","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"d04911d87d","type":"paragraph","text":"“汇报是“密探””。(黄盛业)","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"524462413d","type":"paragraph","text":"“汇报象特务打小报告一样。”(张景明)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"1899f1c020","type":"paragraph","text":"“我反对私人汇报，目的是对党支部，国民党是见面不谈的、形式上不同、实质上没有什么两样。“向党汇报是出卖同志。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"279b05a30c","type":"paragraph","text":"“鉴定只是坐在办公室听汇报，是否可靠，对党员来说还比较好些，有组织生活互相比较了解，对那些不正确的批评和扣帽子，会给予反击和解释，对群众来说，被扣了帽子还不了解，可能使他们背上了包袱。”(钱端升)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"24f07af004","type":"paragraph","text":"黄盛业说：“我吃过鉴定的亏”“毕业时不要党来鉴定。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"},{"id":"9d901cd608","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《北京政法学院右派分子言行汇编》(第1部分)(北京政法学院，1957年10月)。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4"}],"page":{"id":"7c5dd9e70f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6e8b73eea4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}